description: Try our easy to follow Roasted Feta & Tomatoes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Baked cheese,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Traybake,Low sugar,Halal,High protein,Vegetarian,Tomato
name: Roasted Feta & Tomatoes Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 cup Cobram Estate Classic Flavour Extra Virgin Olive Oil
2 tbs fresh thyme sprigs (fresh to serve)

recipeInstructions.text: Place 200g block Greek-style feta, 320g punnet mix-a-mato tomatoes (halved, if large) and 250g cocktail truss tomatoes in a roasting pan.
Drizzle with 1/2 cup Cobram Estate Classic Flavour Extra Virgin Olive Oil.
Season, then bake in an oven preheated to 200°C/180°C fan-forced for 30 minutes or until tomatoes have softened. Cool for 5 minutes.
Top with fresh thyme sprigs and serve with toasted crusty bread.
